name: Veganie
description: Independent, all-vegan beauty care and cosmetics shop est. since 2015 (originally known as Vegan Mania). Features a natural and cruelty-free range of products like body lotion and oils, lip balms, make-up, and nail polish. Open Mon 11:00-19:00, Tue-Sat 10:00-19:00. Closed Sun.

name: Hank Vegan Burger - Archives
description: Hank's flagship location est. since 2013. Features a menu of burgers which are all vegan and delicious. Feb 2019 reported Beyond Burger available. Burgers are served alongside fries, small salads, cookies, and beer. Open Mon-Fri 12:00-22:00, Sat 12:00-23:00, Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Happiz - Monge
description: The second branch of this vegetarian pizzeria opened Jan 2019. Features create-your-own pizzas. Offers mock meats (ham, merguez, salami, chorizo), beyond meat steak pieces, and a variety of fresh vegetable toppings. Has vegan mozzarella cheese. For dessert try the chocolate mousse pot or vegan tiramisu. Open Mon-Sat 11:30-14:30, 18:30-22:30, Sun 11:30-22:30. Closed Mon.

name: Hank Vegan Pizza
description: A vegan pizza shop est. 2016 by Hank Vegan Burger. Offers daily variety of pizzas, which are available by the slice: choose which you'd like. Also serves drinks, salad, and desserts. Seating on two floors. Open Mon-Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Cloud Cakes
description: Vegan coffee shop and bakery near Chatelet-Les Halles station, since 2016. Specialty is cupcakes. Serves coffee and drinks, a selection of light meals, and of course, vegan croissants and pastries. Offers breakfast Monday through Saturday and brunch on Sunday. Lunch is served till 3pm. Open Mon-Fri 09:00-19:00, Sat 09:30-19:00, Sun 11:30-15:30.

name: Wholywood
description: Vegan cafe serving organic food and craft coffee. Features fusion bowls, burgers, sandwiches, "crazy waffles" and other daily selection of fresh baked pastries plus juices and drinks - since May 2019. Plastic-free. Note that some food may start to sell out after 5pm and may close earlier than stated times. Open Mon 09:00-18:00, 10:00-18:00, Wed-Sat 09:00-18:00.

name: Biovégane
description: Healthy vegan burger bar set in a pedestrian area. Can accommodate 10 on the heated terrace and 6 inside. Offering 100% organic and handmade food with gluten-free options. Customise your burger with preferred garnish such as vegan "bacon" or seaweed. Fries are not fried but roasted in the oven with little oil. Est. 2018 formerly as VeganBioBurger and GABY. Open Mon 12:00-14:30, 18:30-21:00, Wed-Fri 12:00-14:30, Wed 18:30-21:00, Thu-Sun 18:30-22:00, Sat-Sun 12:00-15:00.

name: Burger Theory
address: 11 Blvd des Filles du Calvaire, Paris, France, 750…
description: Fast food vegan restaurant opened Sep 2018 in Paris 3rd arrisdonment. Serves multiple flavors of plant-based burgers in addition to accompaniments like fries, salad, and soup of the day. For dessert try the vegan brownie. Combo meal of burger with side, drink, and dessert available. Open Mon-Tue 12:00-15:00, Wed-Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Un Monde Vegan
address: 64 rue Notre Dame de Nazareth, Paris, France, 7500…
description: Un Monde Vegan, meaning "a vegan world," is a 100% vegan retail shop as well as an online store. Features a wide range of plant-based products including packaged and chilled foods, faux meats, vegan cheese, snacks and chocolates. Also has nutritional supplements, food for animals, eco-friendly cleaning and bodycare products. Established since 2009. Open Mon-Tue 11:00-20:00, Wed-Sat 10:00-20:00.

name: Aujourd'hui Demain
description: Vegan concept store & restaurant-cafe est. 2017. Serves Cali inspired lunch foods from 10am-3pm with toasts and seasonal bowls, classic blt cheeseburger w/ beyond meat, and a "fried chicky" burger. In the evenings Tue-Sat from 6pm a Mexican menu is available. On the weekends there is brunch. The coffee shop offers granola bowls, pancakes, latte drinks, juices, and gluten-free pastries. In the store you will find clothing, accessories, books, natural beauty products, and select groceries for sale. Open Tue-Sat 10:00-22:30, Sun 11:00-18:00. Closed Mon.

name: Hot Vog
description: Takeaway vegan eatery with a small seating area, est. 2017 across from the Luxembourg Gardens. Specializes in hot vogs which are vegan hot dogs. Offers also sweets like waffles as well as fresh juices and chilled bottled beverages. Hot Vog also operates food trucks/carts parked at Jardim d'Acclimatation, Parly2 at Le Chesnay, Aeroville, and Grande Épicerie rue de Passy malls. Open Mon-Sun 11:00-20:00. Closes early sometimes.

name: Toutofu
description: Vegan Chinese restaurant in Paris whose name is a portemanteau for tout tofu, which means all tofu. The kitchen makes fresh tofu and soy milk drinks, and the menu features many dishes with tofu. Find choices like savory Chinese pancakes, steamed dumplings, pan-fried dumplings, mapo tofu with side of rice/noodles, noodles with tofu and veggies, dan dan noodles, and grilled tofu. Est. 2014 as vegetarian and switched to all-vegan shortly after. Open Tue-Sat 12:00-15:00, Tue-Sun 19:00-22:00.

name: Hank Vegan Burger - Rochechouart
description: Hank's 2nd branch in Paris opened May 2018. Offers the same popular menu of delicious plant-based burgers, including the beyond burger, alongside fries, small salads, vegan cookies, ice cream, and beer. Casual setting with open kitchen. Beginning Feb 2019 this branch (only) began offering Sunday brunch from 12-3:30pm. The brunch features scrambled “eggs” with mushrooms, salad and guacamole, potatoes, quinoa croissant, stewed apples/pears; yogurt, and toasted bread. Open Mon-Fri 12:00-15:00, 18:00-22:00, Sat-Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Jay & Joy
description: Vegan shop specializing in plant-based cheese from the French brand, Jay & Joy. Other products offered include vegan cheesecake, yogurt, vegan ice cream, and bottled drinks. Accepts pre-orders by phone or mail. La première crèmerie végétale de France. Open Tue-Fri 12:00-19:30, Sat 12:00-19:00, Sun 10:00-14:00.

name: Bulldog Vegan
description: Casual vegan food restaurant serving mezze and fresh salads, burgers and fries, sandwiches, calzones, and Turkish pizza. On Sunday brunch is offered. Beverage options include vegan wine and beer. For dessert try the baklava. Est. 2019. Open Mon-Sat 12:00-14:30, Mon-Thu 18:30-22:00, Fri-Sat 18:30-23:00.

name: Vegan Hero
description: Vegan fast food restaurant offering casual meals like kebabs made from seitan, burritos, burgers, wraps, fries, ice cream and sweets in an industrial atmosphere. Makes all food in-house. Dogs are welcome. Previously named Super Vegan. Open Tue-Sun 12:00-14:00, 19:00-22:00.

name: La Maison Vegane
description: Vegan and organic retail shop est. 2018. Stocking specialty plant-based foods and goods, including vegan cheese and mock meats, non-dairy milks and ice cream, ready-to-eat foods and snacks, plus natural comestics and soaps. Épicerie végétalienne à Puteaux. Open Mon 14:00-20:00, Tue-Sat 10:00-20:00, Sun 10:00-14:00.

name: The Body Shop - Rivoli
description: International chain specializing in natural body and beauty products which are all vegetarian, many vegan, and not tested on animals. Open Mon-Sat 10:00-20:00.

name: Naturalia - Renard
description: Magazin bio. Organic store chain stocking a large selection of products including vegan foods and fresh produce. Open Mon-Sat 10:00-20:00.

description: Serves meat, vegan options available. Serves traditional food from Alsace, mostly flammkuchen (tarte flambé). Open Mon-Sat 12:00-15:00, Mon-Sun 18:00-23:30, Sun 11:30-16:00.

Open Mon-Sun 08:00-22:00.

name: Le Comptoir 18-20

name: Le Tambour d'Arcole

Open Mon 10:00-19:00, Wed 10:00-19:00, Thu 09:00-19:00, Fri 10:00-19:30, Sat 10:30-19:30, Sun 11:00-19:00.

Open Mon-Sun 10:00-20:00.

Open Mon-Sat 15:00-02:00, Sun 15:00-01:00.

Open Mon-Fri 11:00-20:00, Sat-Sun 11:00-21:00.

Open Wed-Sun 12:00-16:00, 19:00-00:00. Last order lunch 3pm, dinner 10:30pm.

name: EXKi - Rambuteau
description: Serves meat, vegan options available. Fast health food concept with outlets in France and Italy. Tagline is "nature's kitchen." Offers grab-n-go sandwiches and salads with vegan options and ingredients listed. Uses some organic produce. Near Centre Pompidou. Open Mon-Sun 07:30-22:30.

name: Cecile et Jeanne
description: This particular Cecile Jeanne store sells the bag collection by the French vegan designer Natacha Seroussi. The bags are vintage inspired and are made with cork leather and colorful cotton oil cloth. Near metro Saint Paul line 1. Open Mon-Fri 11:00-19:00, Sat-Sun 11:00-20:00.

description: Serves meat, vegan options available. Middle Eastern restaurant offering vegan falafel wraps, hummus and mezze dishes. Open Mon-Sun 11:00-00:00.

Two mains of the mains dishes are vegan: a falafel platter and a salad meal with grilled aubergines, radish, walnuts, pomegranate molasses, seeds, and herbs served with side of olives, hummus and a garlic dip, and small flatbreads. Two of the sides are vegan, including pommes de terre which consists of wedges sautéed in coriander and chickpea garlic cream.

address: 37 rue de la Bucherie  , Paris, France, 75005

With both indoor and outdoor tables, the cafe serves coffee, tea, and fresh-squeezed juices, as well as organic, largely (95%) vegetarian food, including George’s lemon pie. Has plenty of clearly labeled (V) vegan choices - try the vegan protein shake. Open Mon-Sun 10:00-20:30.

description: Serves meat, vegan options available. Menu changes on a weekly basis and always offers at least one explicitly vegan dish. Also serves several vegan desserts as well as scones. Open Mon-Fri 10:00-18:00. Closed Sat-Sun.

Open Mon-Sat 12:00-15:00, 19:00-23:00.

name: Aenima Tattoo
description: Vegan tattoo and piercing parlor. Open Mon 14:00-20:00, Tue-Sat 10:00-20:00.

Vegan choices include: tofu and hummus salad, seaweed salad, Indian tahini sandwich, soups, vegetable mixes, quinoa mixes, paella, vegetable croquette, spring rolls, fruit desserts, nut milk. Has a filtered water fountain. Open Mon-Sat 11:30-20:00.

name: Krishna Bhavan - 5eme
description: Vegetarian Indian restaurant with outlets in Paris serving South Indian food. Vegans should ask for dishes without milk dips or yoghurt dips. Open Mon 12:00-23:00, Wed-Sun 12:00-23:00.
